斯里蘭卡北部一家醫院遭到三次砲彈攻擊，造成9人死亡，多人受傷。 _Ramblings of A
Mind_[譴責](http://ramblingsmind.blogspot.com/2009/02/condemn-attacks-on-
hospital.html "http://ramblingsmind.blogspot.com/2009/02/condemn-attacks-on-
hospital.html")對醫院的攻擊行為，
_Chitrangi_[論述](http://chitrangi.wordpress.com/2009/02/02/who-said-the-truth-
icrc-or-army-spokesman/ "http://chitrangi.wordpress.com/2009/02/02/who-said-
the-truth-icrc-or-army-spokesman/")幕後主使可能是誰。

